---

---

<section id="about">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-label">01 / ABOUT</div>
    <div class="section-title">About Me</div>

    <div class="about-layout">
      <div class="about-text">
        <p>
          I'm an electronics engineer and embedded firmware developer based in
          Jakarta, Indonesia. My flagship project — a <strong
            >computer-based 12-lead ECG system</strong
          > — spans analog front-end hardware design, STM32F401 DSP firmware, galvanic
          isolation, and a real-time PC visualization app. Every layer, built from
          scratch.
        </p>
        <p style="margin-top:16px;">
          Professionally, I've spent three years in RPA development and business
          analysis, shipping automation solutions with UiPath for enterprise
          clients. I bridge the gap between hardware-level thinking and business
          process understanding — useful whether I'm reading an ADC datasheet or
          writing a functional specification.
        </p>
        <p style="margin-top:16px;">
          Physics graduate from Universitas Lampung. I also jump into game
          development — I believe good engineers are usually curious people.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="about-aside">
        <div class="about-photo-container">
          <img
            src="/photo.jpg"
            alt="Reyhan Issatyadi Darmawan"
            class="about-photo"
          />
        </div>

        <div class="about-stats">
          <div class="stat-box">
            <div class="stat-num">3+</div>
            <div class="stat-label">Years in Embedded &amp; RPA</div>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-box">
            <div class="stat-num">12</div>
            <div class="stat-label">ECG Leads Acquired</div>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-box">
            <div class="stat-num">2</div>
            <div class="stat-label">MCUs in ECG System</div>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-box">
            <div class="stat-num">BSc</div>
            <div class="stat-label">Physics, Univ. Lampung</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  #about {
    padding-top: 30px;
  }
  .about-layout {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 320px;
    gap: 40px;
    align-items: start;
  }
  .about-text {
    font-size: 0.96rem;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    line-height: 1.85;
  }
  .about-text strong {
    color: var(--amber);
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  .about-aside {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 24px;
  }
  .about-photo-container {
    position: relative;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    overflow: hidden;
    aspect-ratio: 1 / 1;
    background: var(--bg2);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    transition:
      border-color 0.3s,
      box-shadow 0.3s;
  }
  .about-photo {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    transition: transform 0.5s ease;
  }
  .about-photo-container::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    inset: 10px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(202, 213, 226, 0.08);
    pointer-events: none;
    transition: border-color 0.3s;
  }
  .about-photo-container:hover {
    border-color: var(--amber);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
  }
  .about-photo-container:hover .about-photo {
    transform: scale(1.02);
  }
  .about-photo-container:hover::before {
    border-color: rgba(255, 184, 106, 0.25);
  }
  .about-stats {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 12px;
  }
  @media (max-width: 700px) {
    .about-layout {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
